/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536e33c4edfea7858f266c6fabd50ef2e304b3e6","tid":1697951,"uid":198590,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"幾個月前有咩?<br />\n之前我都一早想開POST講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 廢青</strong><br />\n日日淨係識打機, 網上兇恨, 現實碌撚<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/155803_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n但而家呢??<br />\n佢地企出黎對抗暴政<br />\n佢地組織集會, 行動, 怎至係政黨<br />\n冇人再敢話佢地「廢」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6KzGJmuz4UTxov0zGkly2Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190917a165526.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F6KzGJmuz4UTxov0zGkly2Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190917a165526.jpg&h=4f51b1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 港女<br />\n日撚日要食埋D生勾勾 ON99既野<br />\n又日日掛住睇韓星<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSs6lH0lrsce1wGtQmp_tsKYJn0L-gWelQ-j8oNGTgSDm5jvy1f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcSs6lH0lrsce1wGtQmp_tsKYJn0L-gWelQ-j8oNGTgSDm5jvy1f&h=8fc7c9cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但而家呢??<br />\n佢地企出黎, 做文宣, 打國際戰線, 起連儂牆<br />\n「港女」不再係一個貶義詞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LTvUcTY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLTvUcTY.jpg&h=6a589d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 廢老<br />\n日撚日係到梅下梅下, 唔知係到做咩鳩<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/elderly2_T1j8N_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Felderly2_T1j8N_1200x0.png&h=47dbb595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但而家呢??<br />\n我地一般叫佢地做「銀髮族」, 佢地思維比好多人都更清晰<br />\n就算佢地身體不良於行, 幾辛苦佢地都企出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VcScbDlsMwA12n6ylr5p.w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/cd5a3cbe24052e2461430bb7fd37108e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVcScbDlsMwA12n6ylr5p.w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fcd5a3cbe24052e2461430bb7fd37108e&h=45e56b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 港豬<br />\n成埋中產上晒岸咩鳩都唔敢<br />\n日日諗下去食咩食, 睇下港姐, 去下旅行<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pentoy.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA-800x445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pentoy.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA-800x445.jpg&h=585f31ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但而家呢??<br />\n雖然佢地有家庭,有負責,有子女要養<br />\n但佢地成為左「家長」, 拯救我地的「細路」<br />\n教育佢地的「細路」, 成為香港的人家長<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phppNQKJm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phppNQKJm.jpg&h=c5a00728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時代要進步<br />\n香港人一樣<br />\n我好喜歡幾個月前的連登<br />\n日日ON99 恥笑下人<br />\n但係我而家更為珍惜呢個香港"},{"pid":"bf6dfca316348eae0db84a8b2de48e780a618ef1","tid":1697951,"uid":59586,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"536e33c4edfea7858f266c6fabd50ef2e304b3e6","tid":1697951,"uid":198590,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"幾個月前有咩?<br />\n之前我都一早想開POST講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 廢青</strong><br />\n日日淨係識打機, 網上兇恨, 現實碌撚<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/155803_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n但而家呢??<br />\n佢地企出黎對抗暴政<br />\n佢地組織集會, 行動, 怎至係政黨<br />\n冇人再敢話佢地「廢」<br />\n<img src=