%25E4%25BA%25BA-800x445.jpg&h=585f31ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但而家呢??<br />\n雖然佢地有家庭,有負責,有子女要養<br />\n但佢地成為左「家長」, 拯救我地的「細路」<br />\n教育佢地的「細路」, 成為香港的人家長<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phppNQKJm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phppNQKJm.jpg&h=c5a00728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時代要進步<br />\n香港人一樣<br />\n我好喜歡幾個月前的連登<br />\n日日ON99 恥笑下人<br />\n但係我而家更為珍惜呢個香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:32:39.000Z","msg":"We connected <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1301635a6612a10c8c1a01a4e6dd35b5b5b7d64b","tid":1697951,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:33:06.000Z","msg":"港豬"},{"pid":"5a5625a9f94b2f66a2b0c979a815f03681c40e2a","tid":1697951,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T11:22:12.000Z","msg":"fg 50k"}]}